5.2 OUTSTANDING AMOUNT CALCULATION
Do NOT use Principal Amount for Net Worth. Instead calculate:
  Total EMIs = (End Date - Start Date) in months
  EMIs Paid = (Today - Start Date) in months  
  Outstanding = Principal - (EMIs Paid × EMI) 
  [cap Outstanding at 0, never negative]
  Use Outstanding Amount in Net Worth = Assets - Outstanding Liabilities

